org.forgerock.guice.core

Annotation Type GuiceModule


  • @Target(value=TYPE)
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface GuiceModule
    Signifies a Guice module class that should be used to configure the Guice injector when the system starts up. All classes with this annotation must extend Module).
    Since:
    1.0.0
